text: I sent Fabian a pdf with the pictures that I created as front cover., [G:\Meine Ablage\Easy Voice Recorder\2024-01-08-10-24.mp3](file://G:/Meine%20Ablage/Easy%20Voice%20Recorder/2024-01-08-10-24.mp3)

Now Lidl also offers the acquisition of the old device and therefore, as soon as I have a delivery appointment for the new refrigerator, I want to arrange an appointment for the same day of delivery with Schroll, so that he can expand the refrigerator and then the freight company can take the old device with them. Lidl, [G:\Meine Ablage\Easy Voice Recorder\2024-01-08-10-23.mp3](file://G:/Meine%20Ablage/Easy%20Voice%20Recorder/2024-01-08-10-23.mp3)

I was on the phone with Mr. von Fahrer about my heat pump. He said it could be an option to buy two heat pumps in the first year and only in the following year to insulate the building wall, because at the moment, on the one hand, the production capacities of the heat pump manufacturers have increased enormously and the orders have now broken away to large parts due to the uncertainty in the funding regime. And so I could be treated relatively privilegedly as one of the few who ordered. And Mr. von Fahrer checks this. I continued to listen to the contact of Mr. von Fahrer on Handelschneider and phoned him to cancel this contact., [G:\Meine Ablage\Easy Voice Recorder\2024-01-08-11-38.mp3](file://G:/Meine%20Ablage/Easy%20Voice%20Recorder/2024-01-08-11-38.mp3)
